02:03.970 --> 02:08.979
<font size="20"><b>"Reply"</b></font>

02:17.950 --> 02:19.910
<font size="20"><b>That sure is a lot of wagons.</b></font>

02:21.280 --> 02:22.570
<font size="20"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

02:22.570 --> 02:24.200
<font size="20"><b>You don't know?</b></font>

02:24.200 --> 02:27.710
<font size="20"><b>Right now, all the heads of the
military are meeting inside the castle</b></font>

02:27.710 --> 02:30.620
<font size="20"><b>to finally dismantle the Scout Regiment.</b></font>

02:30.620 --> 02:31.710
<font size="20"><b>See?</b></font>

02:31.710 --> 02:34.750
<font size="20"><b>There's the gallows for
hanging their commander.</b></font>

02:35.380 --> 02:38.510
<font size="20"><b>I bet it's ongoing as we speak...
his final judgment.</b></font>

02:39.760 --> 02:45.190
<font size="20"><b>If humanity loses the Scout Regiment,
that means humanity loses their spear.</b></font>

02:46.020 --> 02:51.440
<font size="20"><b>When enemies close in, you guard not with a
shield, but a spear that eliminates the threat.</b></font>

02:52.230 --> 02:56.150
<font size="20"><b>Suppose now, if this instant,
Wall Rose were to be breached...</b></font>

02:57.230 --> 03:01.990
<font size="20"><b>The residents of Wall Rose would again
flee and take refuge in Wall Sina.</b></font>

03:02.570 --> 03:07.830
<font size="20"><b>But the earlier evacuation left stockpiles
with no more than a few days at best.</b></font>

03:08.450 --> 03:13.370
<font size="20"><b>In the blink of an eye, most of the residents
would be forced to fight for survival.</b></font>

03:14.340 --> 03:20.590
<font size="20"><b>Wall Rose and Sina... Humanity would be split
in two factions and civil war would erupt.</b></font>

03:21.630 --> 03:27.330
<font size="20"><b>Even if the wall was not breached, Wall Rose
is continually suffering a food shortage.</b></font>

03:28.060 --> 03:30.890
<font size="20"><b>It may not be Titans that breach Wall Sina...</b></font>

03:31.520 --> 03:35.940
<font size="20"><b>There's a chance the residents
of Wall Rose do it first.</b></font>

03:40.150 --> 03:41.690
<font size="20"><b>Reclaim Wall Maria.</b></font>

03:42.450 --> 03:46.430
<font size="20"><b>If humanity is to ever hope for
a future, that is the only way.</b></font>

03:47.370 --> 03:51.020
<font size="20"><b>Are you implying that the Scouts
are needed for such a cause?</b></font>

03:51.540 --> 03:55.610
<font size="20"><b>Our duty as Scouts has always been
to charge forth at the enemy.</b></font>

03:56.130 --> 03:58.960
<font size="20"><b>Cowering away will not solve anything.</b></font>

04:00.090 --> 04:05.470
<font size="20"><b>Or could it be... you have some sort
of secret plan to overcome this ordeal?</b></font>

04:12.180 --> 04:15.520
<font size="20"><b>Erwin, I don't think you understand.</b></font>

04:15.520 --> 04:19.839
<font size="20"><b>The reason you're here today is not
to discuss our future within the walls,</b></font>

04:20.440 --> 04:23.480
<font size="20"><b>nor is it because of something
as simple as murder.</b></font>

04:24.280 --> 04:26.280
<font size="20"><b>Clause Six, Charter of Humanity.</b></font>

04:26.280 --> 04:30.830
<font size="20"><b>"Thou shall not prioritize one's own
gain over the longevity of humanity."</b></font>

04:31.580 --> 04:33.960
<font size="20"><b>You're here for this grave offense.</b></font>

04:33.960 --> 04:38.630
<font size="20"><b>Indeed. You've refused to hand
over Eren Jaeger multiple times.</b></font>

04:38.630 --> 04:41.550
<font size="20"><b>In doing so, you've violated the Charter.</b></font>

04:41.840 --> 04:44.930
<font size="20"><b>But Eren is vital for reclaiming Wall Maria!</b></font>

04:45.050 --> 04:47.470
<font size="20"><b>That is not for the Scouts to decide!</b></font>

04:47.470 --> 04:50.970
<font size="20"><b>Eren Jaeger is a Titan whose
powers are not understood!</b></font>

04:50.970 --> 04:54.480
<font size="20"><b>Sheltering him within the walls
is a risk to humanity!</b></font>

04:54.480 --> 04:58.620
<font size="20"><b>It's absurd for a single commander
to have control of him alone.</b></font>

04:59.110 --> 05:02.480
<font size="20"><b>And yet, you stubbornly persisted
in some plan of yours.</b></font>

05:02.900 --> 05:07.010
<font size="20"><b>Not only did you feign his abduction
and conceal Eren Jaeger...</b></font>

05:07.530 --> 05:10.330
<font size="20"><b>...but you silenced Dimo Reeves
since he knew of your plans.</b></font>

05:11.160 --> 05:13.200
<font size="20"><b>This is clearly treason.</b></font>

05:13.200 --> 05:17.120
<font size="20"><b>It is not a stretch to say that
you're the threat to humanity.</b></font>

05:18.210 --> 05:19.540
<font size="20"><b>Commander Pyxis.</b></font>

05:19.540 --> 05:20.040
<font size="20"><b>Hmm?</b></font>

05:20.540 --> 05:25.090
<font size="20"><b>The Garrison and Scout Regiments
both risk their lives on the front lines.</b></font>

05:25.090 --> 05:28.300
<font size="20"><b>How are we to know that
you're not his comrade?</b></font>

05:28.680 --> 05:33.560
<font size="20"><b>I'm quite disturbed that you believe
we would align ourselves with the Scouts.</b></font>

05:33.560 --> 05:36.600
<font size="20"><b>Nothing is more senseless
than humans killing humans.</b></font>

05:37.270 --> 05:42.850
<font size="20"><b>In this cramped world that we humans have,
one spark will engulf all in no time.</b></font>

05:43.570 --> 05:46.610
<font size="20"><b>When it came time to defend Trost District,</b></font>

05:46.610 --> 05:50.730
<font size="20"><b>that's what I told my soldiers
before sending many to their deaths.</b></font>

05:51.830 --> 05:55.870
<font size="20"><b>If the Scout Regiment is that one spark,
it should be smothered at once.</b></font>

05:57.500 --> 06:00.460
<font size="20"><b>After all, if the Titans do manage to break</b></font>

06:00.460 --> 06:03.410
<font size="20"><b>the wall and find hardly anyone left inside...</b></font>

06:03.410 --> 06:05.760
<font size="20"><b>...those poor Titans might go hungry.</b></font>

06:08.220 --> 06:09.230
<font size="20"><b>Very well.</b></font>

06:09.720 --> 06:11.250
<font size="20"><b>Allow us to discuss.</b></font>

06:14.520 --> 06:17.240
<font size="20"><b>Your Majesty... May we?</b></font>

06:25.530 --> 06:28.520
<font size="20"><b>Erwin... Is this how you want it to end?!</b></font>

06:37.870 --> 06:41.550
<font size="20"><b>In the name of the King,
I will announce your judgment.</b></font>

06:42.250 --> 06:43.460
<font size="20"><b>Erwin Smith.</b></font>

06:44.340 --> 06:47.880
<font size="20"><b>For violating Clause Six of the Charter of Humanity,</b></font>

06:47.880 --> 06:49.630
<font size="20"><b>you are sentenced to death.</b></font>

06:52.140 --> 06:54.770
<font size="20"><b>Your execution will be carried out immediately.</b></font>

06:55.350 --> 06:56.270
<font size="20"><b>Take him.</b></font>

06:59.560 --> 07:02.100
<font size="20"><b>Is this what you wanted, Erwin?!</b></font>

07:08.900 --> 07:10.610
<font size="20"><b>With this, you're...</b></font>

07:25.710 --> 07:26.710
<font size="20"><b>Wall Rose...</b></font>

07:27.590 --> 07:28.840
<font size="20"><b>...has been breached!</b></font>

07:32.590 --> 07:34.760
<font size="20"><b>The Colossal Titan appeared out of nowhere!</b></font>

07:34.760 --> 07:39.390
<font size="20"><b>Along with the Armored Titan, they broke
through both gates of Calaneth District!</b></font>

07:39.930 --> 07:43.450
<font size="20"><b>Currently, refugees from the East
are flocking here for safety!</b></font>

07:44.980 --> 07:46.760
<font size="20"><b>Establish a route for the evacuees!</b></font>

07:47.480 --> 07:51.860
<font size="20"><b>Have all Garrison troops
converge and defend the East!</b></font>

07:51.860 --> 07:54.160
<font size="20"><b>Get the evacuees safely to Wall Sina!</b></font>

07:54.620 --> 07:57.910
<font size="20"><b>Everyone, hurry! Saving the
evacuees is our top priority!</b></font>

07:58.370 --> 07:58.990
<font size="20"><b>--Sir!</b></font>

07:58.990 --> 07:59.620
<font size="20"><b>--No!
--Sir!</b></font>

08:00.200 --> 08:01.000
<font size="20"><b>Hmm?</b></font>

08:01.210 --> 08:03.960
<font size="20"><b>Close up all of the gates to Wall Sina!</b></font>

08:03.960 --> 08:06.500
<font size="20"><b>Don't let a single refugee inside!</b></font>

08:07.800 --> 08:08.610
<font size="20"><b>Huh?!</b></font>

08:09.550 --> 08:13.300
<font size="20"><b>B-But that's... all the Wall Rose residents?</b></font>

08:14.130 --> 08:17.810
<font size="20"><b>Your command is to sit back and
watch as half of humanity dies?</b></font>

08:17.970 --> 08:21.730
<font size="20"><b>It's just like he said earlier!
That's asking for civil war!</b></font>

08:21.730 --> 08:25.690
<font size="20"><b>We can't let the government lose control!
If that happens, it's over!</b></font>

08:25.850 --> 08:29.940
<font size="20"><b>B-But... That's only a mere possibility!</b></font>

08:29.940 --> 08:32.700
<font size="20"><b>It's enough for that possibility to exist!</b></font>

08:32.700 --> 08:35.500
<font size="20"><b>Our authority is and always will be absolute!</b></font>

08:35.860 --> 08:37.320
<font size="20"><b>Now, get moving!</b></font>

08:45.210 --> 08:45.970
<font size="20"><b>Shit...</b></font>

08:46.420 --> 08:49.550
<font size="20"><b>To think the wall would be
breached at a time like this...</b></font>

08:49.710 --> 08:52.300
<font size="20"><b>Though, there is a silver lining.</b></font>

08:52.300 --> 08:54.050
<font size="20"><b>We've already found the power.</b></font>

08:54.680 --> 08:58.260
<font size="20"><b>All that's left is to bide our time
until the vessel takes it.</b></font>

08:58.720 --> 09:03.640
<font size="20"><b>That's right. There's no need to be
flustered by this little disaster.</b></font>

09:03.640 --> 09:06.600
<font size="20"><b>As long as Wall Sina holds up, we'll be fine.</b></font>

09:06.600 --> 09:09.140
<font size="20"><b>Yes, once Lord Reiss comes back...</b></font>

09:11.610 --> 09:13.940
<font size="20"><b>Let's do it! Close the gates!</b></font>

09:13.940 --> 09:14.860
<font size="20"><b>Wait!</b></font>

09:14.860 --> 09:16.510
<font size="20"><b>It'll be too late if we wait!</b></font>

09:19.370 --> 09:20.970
<font size="20"><b>Who gets to choose?</b></font>

09:21.330 --> 09:22.500
<font size="20"><b>Who decides?</b></font>

09:23.200 --> 09:25.540
<font size="20"><b>What are you doing?! Hurry it up!</b></font>

09:25.540 --> 09:27.540
<font size="20"><b>It'll be treason if you don't!</b></font>

09:30.540 --> 09:31.460
<font size="20"><b>I will not!</b></font>

09:31.590 --> 09:32.210
<font size="20"><b>What?!</b></font>

09:32.670 --> 09:33.480
<font size="20"><b>Hey...</b></font>

09:33.960 --> 09:36.590
<font size="20"><b>I... am a human of Wall Rose!</b></font>

09:37.970 --> 09:40.100
<font size="20"><b>I will not allow the gates to be closed!</b></font>

09:40.100 --> 09:41.010
<font size="20"><b>You fool!</b></font>

09:41.010 --> 09:42.720
<font size="20"><b>I will stand behind him.</b></font>

09:49.150 --> 09:51.400
<font size="20"><b>Dhalis Zachary...</b></font>

09:52.650 --> 09:56.650
<font size="20"><b>Are you surprised at all by
their reaction, Premier Zachary?</b></font>

09:57.950 --> 10:00.030
<font size="20"><b>No... Not a bit.</b></font>

10:00.200 --> 10:02.660
<font size="20"><b>Zachary, what's the meaning of this?!</b></font>

10:03.620 --> 10:06.010
<font size="20"><b>That report just now was a false alarm.</b></font>

10:06.370 --> 10:07.770
<font size="20"><b>Rest assured.</b></font>

10:08.210 --> 10:12.040
<font size="20"><b>At the moment, there has been
no report of a Titan attack.</b></font>

10:12.840 --> 10:14.880
<font size="20"><b>You bastards! What is this farce?!</b></font>

10:15.210 --> 10:17.900
<font size="20"><b>If you want the mastermind, it's me.</b></font>

10:18.260 --> 10:19.230
<font size="20"><b>Pyxis?!</b></font>

10:20.010 --> 10:24.310
<font size="20"><b>It seems most of the Interior Police
are off somewhere or other.</b></font>

10:24.310 --> 10:26.600
<font size="20"><b>I suppose that's quite fortunate.</b></font>

10:26.600 --> 10:27.560
<font size="20"><b>What do you mean?!</b></font>

10:27.850 --> 10:33.730
<font size="20"><b>Earlier, I declared to you that the Garrison
Regiment isn't aligned with the Scout Regiment.</b></font>

10:34.270 --> 10:36.360
<font size="20"><b>But I did forget to mention one thing...</b></font>

10:37.280 --> 10:39.570
<font size="20"><b>I'm not aligned with any of you either.</b></font>

10:40.780 --> 10:44.470
<font size="20"><b>While I do possess some of the
same feelings as Erwin here...</b></font>

10:45.200 --> 10:48.020
<font size="20"><b>...I considered leaving things
up to your government</b></font>

10:48.370 --> 10:52.170
<font size="20"><b>if that were the better choice
for the sake of humanity.</b></font>

10:52.670 --> 10:57.570
<font size="20"><b>You are, after all, much wiser than us
when it comes to Titans and the walls.</b></font>

10:59.050 --> 11:03.410
<font size="20"><b>Supposing you actually cared about
saving as many people as possible,</b></font>

11:03.890 --> 11:07.360
<font size="20"><b>I would have been fine
sending Erwin to the gallows.</b></font>

11:07.850 --> 11:13.760
<font size="20"><b>Of course, depending on your decision,
all of us were prepared to forfeit our heads.</b></font>

11:14.770 --> 11:18.690
<font size="20"><b>However, the answer you've
given us is very clear!</b></font>

11:19.570 --> 11:23.400
<font size="20"><b>We may be ignorant about the Titans
and their powers, but...</b></font>

11:23.910 --> 11:28.540
<font size="20"><b>I daresay, we in our ignorance can save
far more people than you ever could!</b></font>

11:28.540 --> 11:33.040
<font size="20"><b>Y-You're a fool! What do you think
undermining us will accomplish?!</b></font>

11:33.040 --> 11:35.460
<font size="20"><b>The citizens will never listen to you!</b></font>

11:35.960 --> 11:38.800
<font size="20"><b>They'll obey whatever the crown says!</b></font>

11:38.800 --> 11:40.970
<font size="20"><b>The regional lords will have none of this!</b></font>

11:41.220 --> 11:43.810
<font size="20"><b>It seems you don't quite understand.</b></font>

11:44.680 --> 11:46.590
<font size="20"><b>This is no mere threat.</b></font>

11:47.100 --> 11:48.330
<font size="20"><b>It's a coup d'Ã©tat.</b></font>

11:50.680 --> 11:53.750
<font size="20"><b>We've successfully restrained
the Interior Police!</b></font>

11:54.100 --> 11:54.600
<font size="20"><b>Mmm.</b></font>

11:58.280 --> 12:03.320
<font size="20"><b>The thing with soldiers, they'll obey
their superior officer over the king.</b></font>

12:03.740 --> 12:06.450
<font size="20"><b>Especially when the king in question is a fraud.</b></font>

12:06.780 --> 12:09.700
<font size="20"><b>We will put in place a new ruler of our own.</b></font>

12:10.200 --> 12:12.200
<font size="20"><b>It can't be... They're actually...</b></font>

12:13.670 --> 12:16.340
<font size="20"><b>Don't even think you can
get away with this hoax!</b></font>

12:16.540 --> 12:18.750
<font size="20"><b>If that disaster had in fact happened...</b></font>

12:19.130 --> 12:23.430
<font size="20"><b>The decision that all of you made violates
Clause Six of the Charter of Humanity.</b></font>

12:24.640 --> 12:27.050
<font size="20"><b>Furthermore, is installing a fake king</b></font>

12:27.050 --> 12:30.980
<font size="20"><b>to personally control and run the
government not punishable by death?</b></font>

12:38.860 --> 12:40.820
<font size="20"><b>Shit! Wake up, dotard!</b></font>

12:40.820 --> 12:42.070
<font size="20"><b>What? Time to eat?</b></font>

12:42.320 --> 12:44.270
<font size="20"><b>Shut up, you useless oaf!</b></font>

12:51.660 --> 12:52.490
<font size="20"><b>Erwin...</b></font>

12:53.210 --> 12:54.500
<font size="20"><b>This is your victory.</b></font>

12:56.080 --> 12:57.200
<font size="20"><b>Aren't you happy?</b></font>

12:58.960 --> 12:59.660
<font size="20"><b>Nile.</b></font>

13:00.840 --> 13:03.110
<font size="20"><b>Humanity has just begun down a new path...</b></font>

13:03.800 --> 13:05.550
<font size="20"><b>One far more dangerous than before.</b></font>

13:24.780 --> 13:27.780
<font size="20"><b>And there you have it.
The coup d'Ã©tat was successful.</b></font>

13:28.240 --> 13:32.160
<font size="20"><b>Premier Zachary has control of
the capital and administrative district.</b></font>

13:32.700 --> 13:36.120
<font size="20"><b>For the time being, the nobility hasn't rebelled.</b></font>

13:36.120 --> 13:38.630
<font size="20"><b>What about the Boss Reeves incident?</b></font>

13:39.040 --> 13:41.840
<font size="20"><b>We got a confession that proved
the charges unfounded.</b></font>

13:42.300 --> 13:44.630
<font size="20"><b>His son Flegel really pulled through big time.</b></font>

13:44.970 --> 13:46.800
<font size="20"><b>Don't you get it?!</b></font>

13:46.800 --> 13:50.140
<font size="20"><b>The government doesn't give
a shit about saving any of us!</b></font>

13:50.140 --> 13:53.220
<font size="20"><b>Face the truth now, because it'll be
too late when you're dead!</b></font>

13:53.220 --> 13:58.980
<font size="20"><b>That's right! If Titans attack us again,
there'll be nothing left this time!</b></font>

13:58.980 --> 14:01.080
<font size="20"><b>Not the company! Not our families!</b></font>

14:01.650 --> 14:04.500
<font size="20"><b>Let's print the truth before that happens!</b></font>

14:06.110 --> 14:11.270
<font size="20"><b>Just like it's written right there, it shows the
charges were bogus, they abused their power,</b></font>

14:11.660 --> 14:14.370
<font size="20"><b>and that King Fritz was a total fake.</b></font>

14:15.200 --> 14:18.300
<font size="20"><b>All our actions were justified self-defense.</b></font>

14:18.790 --> 14:22.070
<font size="20"><b>In other words, we're free people now.</b></font>

14:26.010 --> 14:30.140
<font size="20"><b>Woohoo!</b></font>

14:30.140 --> 14:32.890
<font size="20"><b>No... This can't be...</b></font>

14:33.680 --> 14:35.500
<font size="20"><b>Looks like the gamble paid off.</b></font>

14:35.980 --> 14:36.730
<font size="20"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

14:37.480 --> 14:39.310
<font size="20"><b>It wasn't just Erwin though.</b></font>

14:40.190 --> 14:43.650
<font size="20"><b>The lone choices of many
managed to change the world.</b></font>

14:46.530 --> 14:49.580
<font size="20"><b>And I managed to kill the
three people you loaned me.</b></font>

14:50.660 --> 14:51.610
<font size="20"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

14:55.120 --> 14:57.630
<font size="20"><b>The thing is, part of the Interior Police,</b></font>

14:57.630 --> 15:01.840
<font size="20"><b>their leader, Eren, and Historia are somewhere else.</b></font>

15:01.840 --> 15:03.590
<font size="20"><b>If we don't find them soon...</b></font>

15:05.250 --> 15:06.910
<font size="20"><b>I may have a clue about that.</b></font>

15:08.220 --> 15:11.590
<font size="20"><b>Let's get there and put an end to this battle.</b></font>

15:11.970 --> 15:16.970
